OL,6,FA "dangerous predator" who threatened
OL,7,Fto decapitate a woman he had raped if
OL,8,Fshe reported him to the police has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FJerome Macalla forced his way into the
OL,12,Fwoman's home in Sheffield before
OL,13,Fsexually assaulting her.
OL,15,FThe 33-year-old told his victim he
OL,16,Fwould shoot her, according to South
OL,17,FYorkshire Police.
OL,19,FHe also said he would "take her head
OL,20,Foff" if police came to arrest him.
