OL,10,FOfficers arrested Macalla at her house
OL,11,Fafter he was found with a shovel
OL,12,Fattempting to break in.
OL,14,FPC Katie Walker, the officer in charge
OL,15,Fof the case, said: "Macalla's threats
OL,16,Fwere so menacing and chilling, his
OL,17,Fvictim was left frightened of
OL,18,Freporting the rape to us.
